ra products. It also provides field support, infra managed, and green energy solutions; and electronics manufacturing, electronics repair, and e-auction services. The company serves BFSI, retail, logistics, and public sector industries. The company was formerly known as TVS eTechnology Limited and changed its name to TVS Electronics Limited in December 2003. TVS Electronics Limited was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Chennai, India."}}